{
  "id": "gen-polar-rainbow-explosion",
  "name": "Polar Rainbow Explosion",
  "category": "generative",
  "url": "shaders/gen-polar-rainbow-explosion.wgsl",
  "description": "A polar coordinate explosion enriched with Wolfram spherical shock-wave dynamics. Bass triggers radial shock fronts; treble injects high-frequency ripple. Mouse directs the explosion origin. Full upgraded-rgba stack with ACES tone mapping, temporal feedback, chromatic aberration, and semantic alpha.",
